	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p>You transform into an hybrid humanoid and air elemental form, crackling with electricity and surrounded by whipping winds. Your form shifts, transforming back and forth from solid to gas.</p><p><strong>Bonus Action</strong> - Self - 10 Minutes - @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.Ik6ei7V7ryr5XVoe]{3 Sorcery Points} - Magical</p><p>You choose whether your equipment falls to the ground in your space, merges into your new form, or if you continue to visibly wear it.</p><ul><li><p>You have a fly (hover) speed of 40 ft.</p></li><li><p>You are resistant to &amp;reference[lightning] damage.</p></li><li><p>You are immune to &amp;reference[poison] damage and the &amp;reference[poisoned] condition.</p></li><li><p>You are immune to the &amp;reference[grappled], &amp;reference[petrified], and &amp;reference[restrained] conditions.</p></li><li><p>You weigh close to nothing and can squeeze through gaps as small as 1 inch wide.</p></li><li><p>You no longer have normal bodily functions. You don't breathe, can't bleed, be magically aged, or otherwise do anything that relies on your normal biological functions.</p></li></ul><p>You can revert to your normal form using a bonus action. You also revert to your normal form if you are reduced to 0 hit points.</p>",
